Module tagtraum.japlscript
Package com.tagtraum.japlscript.language

Class TypeClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tagtraum.japlscript.language.TypeClass
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Codec<Reference>, Reference

    public class TypeClass
extends Object
implements Reference, Codec<Reference>
    Describes an AppleScript class at runtime. It lets you find out its superclass(es) and whether an instance is an instance of a certain the type described by this class. You may lookup TypeClass instances via their full name or via their AppleScript 4char code.
    Author:
    Hendrik Schreiber
